Package w16cs350.datatype

Contains the project-specific datatypes shared throughout the system.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    A_LatitudeLongitude
    Defines the shared elements of latitude and longitude encoded in NMEA 0183 format.
    A_Shape
    Defines the shared elements of all geometric shapes that consist of a single path from a start position to an end position.
    Angle
    Defines a navigational angle.
    CoordinatesDelta
    Defines coordinates in an arbitrary coordinate system with arbitrary units.
    CoordinatesScreen
    Defines coordinates in a standard graphics coordinate system with pixel units.
    CoordinatesWorld
    Defines coordinates in a world coordinate system of latitude and longitude.
    Latitude
    Defines latitude encoded in NMEA 0183 format.
    Longitude
    Defines longitude encoded in NMEA 0183 format.
    ShapeArc
    Defines a clockwise arc.
    ShapeLine
    Defines a straight line.
